data.physical_description: The character has a simple, rounded oval head outlined in red. The face features two small blue dots for eyes and a wide, upward-curving red line for a smile. Radiant yellow, spiky lines extend upwards and outwards from the top and sides of the head, resembling a crown or a halo of sunshine. The body is an elongated, rectangular shape, with no distinct legs visible. Two simple, curved arms extend horizontally from the upper red section of the body, each ending in three small, rounded bumps that suggest fingers or mittens.
data.clothing_description: The character wears a long, multi-tiered garment. The upper body consists of a solid red, long-sleeved top or bodice, filled with horizontal red crayon strokes. A single small black dot is placed in the center of the chest area. The lower body, resembling a skirt, is composed of four distinct horizontal tiers, stacked one above the other, each separated by a horizontal line and filled with a different solid color. From top to bottom, these tiers are: 1) Solid yellow, filled with yellow crayon strokes, featuring three small black dots arranged vertically down its center. 2) Solid green, filled with green crayon strokes, also with three small black dots arranged vertically down its center. 3) Solid blue, filled with blue crayon strokes, with three small black dots arranged vertically down its center. 4) Solid orange, filled with orange crayon strokes, also with three small black dots arranged vertically down its center. These black dots resemble buttons.
key_features: Single black dot on the red bodice
data.personality_vibe: Cheerful, friendly, vibrant, and possibly regal or adventurous. The wide smile and bright colors suggest a happy and optimistic disposition.
